* 
Release 2.12 Start 21/05/2020
- 12/09/2020
01. hier.c: use 0755 for bin and sbin
02. indimail-mta: replaced setup with installer which uses text files for installation
03. indimail-mta.spec: fixed AutoReq
- 13/09/2020
04. indimail-mta.spec: updated compiler flags for ucspi-tcp
05. ucspi-tcp: replaced setup with installer which uses text files for installation
06. ucspi-tcp: updated compiler switches
07. instcheck.c: skip chmod if mode is -1
08. hier.c: leave owner, group, permissions alone as they are owned by
    indimail-mta package
09. installer.c: sync permissions with indimail-mta.spec file
- 14/09/2020
10. fixed linkat(), unlinkat(), renameat() calls
- 15/09/2020
11. leapsecs.txt: added date 2016-12-31
12. moved to libqmail:  mess822.h, mess822_addr.c, mess822_date.c,
    mess822_fold.c, mess822_line.c, mess822_ok.c, mess822_quote.c,
    mess822_token.c, mess822_when.c, mess822.3 mess822_addr.3,
    mess822_date.3, mess822_fold.3, mess822_quote.3, mess822_token.3,
    mess822_when.3
13. moved to libqmail: commands.c, commands.h, rewritehost.c, rewritehost.h,
    rewritehost.3
14. smtpd.c, ofmpid.c: variable ctl_maxcmdlen moved to libqmail
15. moved to libqmail: sconfig.c, sconfig.h
16. qmail-send.c, qmail-todo.c: use control files conf-fsync, conf-syncdir
    to turn on fsync, bsd style syncdir semantics
17. qmail-send.c, qmail-todo.c: set / unset USE_FSYNC, USE_SYNCDIR env
    variables
18. qmail-queue.c, qmail-local.c: changed default value of use_fsync,
    use_syncdir to -1
- 16/09/2020
19. indimail-mta, ucspi-tcp: fixes for FreeBSD
- 17/09/2020
20. svctool, create_services, update_tmprsadh, config-fast: fixes for FreeBSD
- 19/09/2020
21. exploit svscan as session leader. Terminate all children using svc -G
22. svcscan_rc: rc startup script for FreeBSD
23. portable Makefile for Linux, FreeBSD, OSX
24. qmailctl: use daemon to start svscan in supervised mode
- 20/09/2020
25. tcpserver.c: open ipv4, ipv6 sockets on FreeBSD and use select before accept()
26. cronlist.q: skip run-cleanq if qscanq service is not installed
- 22/09/2020
27. create_service: fixed certificate path for poppass, indisrvr service
28. use conf-cc-SYSTEM, conf-ld-SYSTEM for system specific CFLAGS, LDFLAGS
29. qmailctl: removed use of initsvc for start/stop
- 24/09/2020
30. Makefile - indimail-mta, ucspi-tcp: split into variables, main Makefile and
    system specific Makefile. New script qmake to do the build
- 25/09/2020
31. syncdir.c: FreeBSD port (use sys/syscall.h)
32. svctool: use --defaults-file=indimail.cnf for shutdown script to avoid
    issues on FreeBSD
33. removed libwatch service
34. run svctool --fixsharedlibs during MySQL startup
35. DIRS: use relative links in /var/indimail
- 26/09/2020
36. svctool: allow setting of MySQL indimail, admin password, indimail UNIX password by
    setting MYSQL_PASS, PRIV_PASS, ADMIN_PASS in env
- 27/09/2020
37. svctool, envmigrate: fixed handling of failure in imap/pop3 service
creation
38. indimail-mta.spec: rpmlint fixes for danglin-relative-symlinks
39. new command svwait to wait for supervise service to come up
40. svctool: make inlookup,pwdlookup service wait for 30 seconds since MySQL services
    comes up
41. svctool: replace /bin/false with /usr/bin/false on FreeBSD
42. sys-checkpwd.c: restore '@' sign in username for authmodules in the chain
43. sys-checkpwd.c: skip stripping of domain if STRIP_DOMAIN env variable is
    not set
- 28/09/2020
44. Makefile: fix perl path in perl scripts
45. removed unused programs - qmail-lagcheck, qmail-lint, elq, pinq, qail
46. added debug statments in sys-checkpwd
47. svctool: added all available authmodules as IMAPMODULES
- 30/09/2020
48. syncdir.c, syncdir.h, qmail-local.c, qmail-queue.c, qmail-send.c,
    qmail-todo.c: Darwin port for syncdir
49. domainkeys.c: define memcpy, strcasecmp, strncasecmp only if not defined
- 02/10/2020
50. installer.c: set permissions for directory only if it is a new directory
51. install indimail.plist in shareddir/boot
52. svctool: updated macOSuseradd, macOSgroupadd
- 03/10/2020
53. svctool, svwait: fix date command syntax for Darwin, FreeBSD
54. svctool: --fixedharedlibs for Darwin
55. svctool: use /bin/echo -n instead of builtin echo -n (which doesn't work on Darwin)
56. svctool: create /var/run/mysqld for Darwin when creating mysqldb
57. svctool: use openssl passwd -6 (sha512) missing on darwin use openssl passwd -1 (md5)
58. svctool: use LC_ALL=C for tr command on Darwin
59. svctool: check for mysqld in mysqlprefix/bin for Darwin
60. svctool: updated macOSuseradd, macOSgroupadd functiona for Darwin
61. svctool: fixed date command for getting time in seconds for Darwin/FreeBSD
62. indimail.plist: service directory on Darwin changed to
    /usr/local/etc/indimail/service
- 04/10/2020
63. svctool: renamed launchd unit file indimail.plist to svscan.plist
    create /service link in /etc/synthetic.conf for Darwin
    create /var/indimail/inquery directory
    removed hardcoded directory for svwait in inlookup, pwdlookup service
64. hier.c, indimail-mta.spec, Makefile: renamed launchd unit file indimail.plist
    to svscan.plist
65. svwait: replace builtin echo with /bin/echo -n (for Darwin)
66. svctool: fixed users getting added multiple times to com.apple.loginwindow
    HiddenUsersList
- 05/10/2020
67. installer new features, 1. uninstall option (-u, -i), 2. create devices,
    3. create fifo
68. Makefile: Added uninstall target
69. Added comments in installer input files
70. svctool: remove indimail, indimail-mta users from HiddenUsersList for
    Darwin
71. Makefile: run instcheck to set permissions on make install.
-06/10/2020
72. indimail-mta: Makefile: replaced g++ with c++ for portability
73. indimail-mta, ucspi-tcp: fixed uninstall target
74. installer.c: fixed setting of symbolic links
75. svctool (freebsd): fix for libmysqlclient on freebsd.
76. svctool (freebsd): remove svscan config/rc file with --config=rm-boot
77. qmail-local.c: fixed bug with loopcounter in qmail-local.c - initialized
    maxdeliveredto
-08/10/2020
78. svscan, supervise, svc, svstat, svok - use /run or /var/run on systems that support it
79. Makefile: added run_init.o object for svc, svstat, svok
80. Makefile: use conf-runfs to configure daemontools to use /run, /var/run
81. ucspi-tcp/ip6_fmt.c: Fixed bug - Erwin Hoffman
-09/10/2020
82. qlocal_upgrade.sh: migrate /service to libexecdir
83. svscan.c, qmailctl, svscan_rc - renamed svscan.pid to .svscan.pid
-10/10/2020
84. smtpd.c: auth functions made static
85. qmail-remote.c: digest_md5() renamed to qr_digest_md5() to avoid clash
86. removed functions duplicated in libqmail
